{"data": [{"id": "4745330", "title": "Tesla: It's Finally Time To Trim (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Tesla Inc offices and production facility in Silicon Valley\" data-id=\"1288508387\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Sundry Photography/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I've covered <b>Tesla, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSLA\" title=\"Tesla, Inc.\">TSLA</a></span>) several times in the past. My initial article offered a $412 fair value estimate of the stock and discussed how Tesla is <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4585346-tesla-electrifying-the-earth\">electrifying the earth</a> and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1288508387/image_1288508387.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745330-tesla-finally-time-to-trim-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 17:49:12"}, {"id": "4745327", "title": "Drone Wars: Building An All-Drone Stock Portfolio For The Future Of Innovation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A flying drone\" data-id=\"956306692\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6674px\" height=\"5338px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Yagi Studio</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>What's going on?</h2> <p><span>For those like myself who are <a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/politics/fbi-warns-new-jersey-residents-not-shoot-down-drones-point-lasers-aircraft\" rel=\"nofollow\">keeping abreast</a> of this topic, drones are swarming the New Jersey/NYC area. Many theories of their purpose are floating around, from trying to sniff hazardous materials, to foreign adversaries, hobbyists, or a possible stress</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/956306692/image_956306692.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745327-drone-wars-building-an-all-drone-stock-portfolio-for-the-future-of-innovation", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 17:30:48"}, {"id": "4745334", "title": "Markets Focus On Reflation Risk After Fed Cuts Rates", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345365014/image_1345365014.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"global stats office\" data-id=\"1345365014\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345365014/image_1345365014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345365014/image_1345365014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345365014/image_1345365014.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345365014/image_1345365014.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345365014/image_1345365014.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345365014/image_1345365014.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345365014/image_1345365014.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345365014/image_1345365014.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Laurence Dutton</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>There are several reasons for adopting a cautious near-term outlook for markets, and reflation risk is arguably at the top of the list. That's <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743288-downshift-us-inflation-stalling\" rel=\"noopener\">old news,</a> but it's a topic that's keenly in focus after the Federal Reserve</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1345365014/image_1345365014.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745334-markets-focus-on-reflation-risk-after-fed-cuts-rates", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 17:20:00"}, {"id": "4745276", "title": "Interested In Retirement Income? This Is Why SCHD Should Be Your Core Step", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324679830/image_1324679830.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Young woman and man climbing red bar graph\" data-id=\"1324679830\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"8660px\" height=\"5773px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324679830/image_1324679830.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324679830/image_1324679830.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324679830/image_1324679830.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324679830/image_1324679830.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324679830/image_1324679830.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324679830/image_1324679830.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324679830/image_1324679830.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324679830/image_1324679830.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Klaus Vedfelt</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Investing and specific security selection can take many forms depending on what kind of objectives are set. If the objective is to beat the market or maximize potential returns irrespective of underlying probability for permanently losing capital, then most</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1324679830/image_1324679830.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745276-interested-in-retirement-income-this-is-why-schd-should-be-your-core-step", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 17:15:00"}, {"id": "4745320", "title": "Tesla: Get Out At The Top (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"One red umbrella at center of multiple black umbrellas\" data-id=\"167532036\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Martin Barraud/OJO Images via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Tesla, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSLA\" title=\"Tesla, Inc.\">TSLA</a></span>)\u2019s shares have passed their previous 3-year-old highs amid a massive post-election surge that has lifted the EV maker\u2019s valuation to ~$1.5T. While I have been optimistic about Tesla\u2019s recovery</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167532036/image_167532036.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745320-tesla-get-out-at-the-top-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 17:09:38"}, {"id": "4744579", "title": "Buy The Dip: 2 REITs Getting Way Too Cheap", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"phrase buy the dip handwritten on night wet window glass surface\" data-id=\"1289941019\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5472px\" height=\"3648px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">z1b</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>President-elect Trump just won the election and it is causing a lot of volatility in the REIT market.</p> <p>Some of our positions are surging while others are taking a hit, resulting in opportunities to buy the dip. </p> <p>Here</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1289941019/image_1289941019.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4744579-buy-the-dip-2-reits-getting-way-too-cheap", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 17:00:00"}, {"id": "4745331", "title": "Bank of England Stays On Hold, But A Dovish Front Is Building", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"The Bank of England in London\" data-id=\"173224046\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5616px\" height=\"3744px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">kelvinjay</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By <a href=\"https://think.ing.com/author/francesco-pesole/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Francesco Pesole</a></em></p> <p>The Bank of England kept the Bank Rate at 4.75% today, as widely expected. Forward guidance remained very cautious and data-dependent, and the Monetary Policy Committee is explicitly refusing to commit to the size and timing of rate cuts in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/173224046/image_173224046.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745331-bank-of-england-stays-hold-dovish-front-building", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 16:55:00"}, {"id": "4745316", "title": "United Natural Foods: Why Is It Going Up?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://media.gettyimages.com/id/924012254/photo/fresh-vegetables-in-warehouse.jpg?b=1&amp;s=612x612&amp;w=0&amp;k=20&amp;c=EHZNNsfJLw7G2B0_W8s7tvawDCc6DdblAqS0Nb_DxMg=\" alt=\"Fresh vegetables in warehouse\" data-id=\"924012254\" data-type=\"getty-image\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">bluecinema/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><span>In less than a year, United Natural Foods (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UNFI\" title=\"United Natural Foods, Inc.\">UNFI</a></span>) has run from under $10 to $27 a share, providing an exceptional return for investors. Given the stock has exhibited relatively muted increases in EBITDA over last year\u2019s trough, some</span></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745316-united-natural-foods-why-is-it-going-up", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 16:51:04"}, {"id": "4745314", "title": "Sustainability And The Investment Case: Heavy Industry", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial view of country road under construction\" data-id=\"1316313214\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1023px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">SimonSkafar/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>By Benedict Buckley, CFA, Dimitry Dayen, CFA, Adam Meyers</p> <p>Thinking of sustainability and the fundamental investment process together makes sense, as sustainability factors should reinforce a strong fundamental case for owning equity securities, either as a source</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316313214/image_1316313214.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745314-sustainability-and-the-investment-case-heavy-industry", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 16:46:16"}, {"id": "4745326", "title": "Rolls-Royce: Service Margin Opportunity", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Rolls Royce Merlin aero engine\" data-id=\"492400245\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andy_Oxley</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>I initially covered Rolls-Royce Holdings plc (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RYCEY\" title=\"Rolls-Royce Holdings plc\">OTCPK:RYCEY</a>) in <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4700975-rolls-royce-room-for-earnings-upgrades\">June of this year</a> with a positive view on their turnaround, which has continued with the company delivering on guidance and re-instating dividends as well as reducing debt. I</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/492400245/image_492400245.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745326-rolls-royce-service-margin-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-19 16:40:00"}]}